_spawnNotesBaseCommand: execute if score #BlockSaberGlobal Difficulty matches {0} run function {1}:{2}
_scoreboardCommand:
scoreboard objectives add {0} dummy
execute as @a unless score #BlockSaberGlobal {0} = #BlockSaberGlobal {0} run scoreboard players set #BlockSaberGlobal {0} 0
_playCommands:
scoreboard players set #BlockSaberGlobal Difficulty {0}
execute as @s run function {1}:play
_spawnOriginCommands: execute if score #BlockSaberGlobal Difficulty matches {1} at @e[type=armor_stand,tag=playerOrgin] run summon armor_stand ~-0.45 ~2.2 ~{0:F18} {{Tags:[nodeSpawnOrigin,blocksaber],DisabledSlots:4096,Invisible:1b,NoGravity:1b,Marker:1b,Invulnerable:1b,Small:1b}}
_playSongCommand: execute if score #BlockSaberGlobal TickCount matches {0} in minecraft:the_end run playsound minecraft:{1} music @a 0 150.0 500 1
_baseCommand: execute if score #BlockSaberGlobal TickCount matches {0}..{1} run function {2}:{3}
_wallCommand:
execute if score #BlockSaberGlobal TickCount matches {0} at @e[type=armor_stand, tag=nodeSpawnOrigin] run teleport @e[type=armor_stand, tag=nodeCursor] ~{1} ~{2} ~{3:F18}
execute if score #BlockSaberGlobal TickCount matches {0} as @e[type=armor_stand, tag=nodeCursor] run function _types:{4}
_scoreCommand: execute if score #BlockSaberGlobal TickCount matches {0} run scoreboard players set #BlockSaberGlobal NodeRowID {1}
_nodePositionCommand: execute if score #BlockSaberGlobal TickCount matches {0} at @e[type=armor_stand, tag=nodeSpawnOrigin] run teleport @e[type=armor_stand, tag=nodeCursor] ~{1} ~{2} ~{3:F18}
_nodeTypeCommand: execute if score #BlockSaberGlobal TickCount matches {0} as @e[type=armor_stand, tag=nodeCursor] run function _types:{1}
_finishedObstacles: execute if score #BlockSaberGlobal TickCount matches {0} run scoreboard players set #BlockSaberGlobal FinishedObsicles 1
_finishedNotes: execute if score #BlockSaberGlobal TickCount matches {0} run scoreboard players set #BlockSaberGlobal FinishedNotes 1
_completedSong: execute if score #BlockSaberGlobal FinishedCount matches 1 if score #BlockSaberGlobal Difficulty matches {0} run scoreboard players set #BlockSaberGlobal {1} 1
_displayTitle: execute if score #BlockSaberGlobal {0} = #BlockSaberGlobal {0} as @e[type=armor_stand,tag=showTitle,tag=blocksaber,tag=!{1}] run function {2}:display_title
